#
# Freestyle
# Button to GPIO port # mapping
#    +---------+
# 1 +|         |
#    |         |+ 7
#    |         |
#20 +|   LCD   |+ 4
#    |         | + 6
# 8 +|         |+ 5
#    |         |
#    |         |+----Power On/Off (connected to PMU)
#    +---------+
#          +9
#        +12 +10
#          +11
# (PCIC-ISA : 23)
